cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to detect satirical news. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural networks and attention mechanisms, which are common in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves analyzing large datasets, which is relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with the potential harm caused by satirical news, which could be relevant to cs.CY (Computers and Society).
